data.description: Welcome Home! Nestled within the serene confines of Newark, Delaware's coveted Belltown Woods neighborhood, this well-maintained two-story residence seamlessly blends modern comfort with classic charm. This inviting 4-bedroom, 2-and-a-half-bathroom home is a testament to thoughtful design and thoughtful upgrades, offering a perfect haven for families seeking both style and functionality.  Boasting a fresh and updated exterior, this residence features recently replaced siding and roof, both upgraded in 2021. As you approach, the manicured lawn and weel-kept landscaping create a picturesque welcome, setting the tone for the inviting atmosphere within.  Step through the front door into a bright and airy foyer, where natural light dances across the gleaming floors. The heart of the home unfolds in the living spaces, where a fully equipped kitchen connects to the dining area. This creates an ideal space for both intimate family dinners and lively gatherings with friends.  Ascend the staircase to discover a master bedroom suite, complete with its own en-suite bathroom, providing a private and comfortable retreat. Three additional bedrooms offer versatility for a growing family or the possibility of creating a home office or hobby room. The remaining full bathroom boasts contemporary fixtures and a clean design.  The property's full basement adds an extra layer of convenience, providing ample storage space or the potential for future expansion, catering to the dynamic needs of its residents.  Outdoors, the backyard, framed by the recently updated siding, invites residents to enjoy the tranquility of nature. This delightful abode is not just a house; it features a large deck for entertainment.  Located in the desirable Belltown Woods neighborhood, this residence offers proximity to local parks, schools, and shopping, making it an ideal choice for those seeking an upgraded, move-in-ready home in Newark, Delaware. Embrace the allure of modern living in this meticulously updated 4-bedroom, 2-and-a-half-bathroom haven, where every detail reflects a commitment to quality and comfort.  Home is Sold As-is
